Business Brief -- Gantos Inc.:
   January Sales Climbed 19%;
   Same-Store Sales Rose 21%
Sales for the year ended Feb. 1 rose 5% to $257.9 million
from $246.3 million during the year-ago period. Same-store
sales increased 1%.
   All sales figures have been adjusted to exclude net sales
from catalog operations, which were discontinued during the
first quarter of 1991.